<i>Christiane, where are you?</i>

1:45:12.917 --> 1:45:17.158
<i>Where are you, children?</i>

1:45:19.067 --> 1:45:23.269
<i>Christiane, where are you?</i>

1:45:24.234 --> 1:45:28.446
<i>Christiane, where are you?</i>

1:45:28.793 --> 1:45:32.853
<i>Where are you, children?</i>

1:45:35.345 --> 1:45:39.085
<i>Christiane, where are you?</i>

1:45:39.791 --> 1:45:43.197
<i>Christiane, where are you?</i>

1:45:46.549 --> 1:45:50.184
<i>Where are you, children?</i>

1:45:58.932 --> 1:46:00.946
<i>Mom, it's me, Gabriel.</i>

1:46:05.753 --> 1:46:07.407
<i>Christiane?</i>

1:46:19.585 --> 1:46:21.332
<i>Christiane.</i>

1:46:21.763 --> 1:46:25.885
<i>Christiane, where are you?</i>

1:46:28.618 --> 1:46:32.646
<i>Christiane, where are you?</i>

1:46:34.216 --> 1:46:39.439
<i>Where are you, children?</i>

1:46:40.028 --> 1:46:42.498
<i>Christiane, where are you?</i>

1:46:42.625 --> 1:46:43.957
<i>Ana...</i>

1:46:44.391 --> 1:46:46.514
<i>Mom is here.</i>

1:46:47.243 --> 1:46:50.203
<i>All the years we've been looking for her,
and three months ago...</i>

1:46:50.309 --> 1:46:52.504
<i>she returned to our old house
and lived there.</i>

1:46:52.634 --> 1:46:57.179
<i>I will stay in Bujumbura to take care of her.
I will wait for her condition to improve.</i>

1:46:57.592 --> 1:47:00.209
<i>Try to get here when you can.</i>
